The Dark Occultis a psychological driven horror game that puts
players in a constant state of anxiety that crescendos into raw
panic and terror. The game takes place in a decaying manor with
demonic entities and strong ties to the occult. You will encounter
grotesque creatures, who will take your life at any moment. Your
only goal -- survive. InThe Dark Occult, players will enter the
game exploring a seemingly abandoned house that is consumed with
demonic activity

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/921780/
